{"tid":830880,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"麥當勞薯條係咪所有size都係得半包","createTime":"2018-09-21T13:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T15:18:48.000Z","uid":103237,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d2d8ee75b76d50fd53136c3d40c60ebaf23c2255","tid":830880,"uid":103237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T13:11:53.000Z","msg":"買包細薯條友特登拎番d薯條搞到得半包"},{"pid":"52b625fde2503d6356e1ffbcf7f87afdd445e111","tid":830880,"uid":182317,"like":16,"dislike":6,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T13:43:33.000Z","msg":"我之前係麥當勞打工既，而我產薯條原則就係咁：<br />\n「屌你老母塞爆」<br />\n無錯呀，就係屌你老母塞爆，我就唔撚理咩公司虧錢，次次產薯條就係老母咁大包。細薯產成大薯，中薯產到巨薯。大薯產到買一送一，其實同個炸薯條個位既薯條全部送俾你一樣。<br />\n<br />\n我仲好記得，我有個月返左25日工，經理過黎同我講，呢個月薯條虧損左26箱，你知唔知咩事？<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母我撚知咩。"},{"pid":"0ef479d18859b46db29912ccc7a55d224ab31fab","tid":830880,"uid":173723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T13:49:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"479db19fa9ebf57f609263009036447fa4d31258","tid":830880,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T14:11:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Hb6HX3R_QVE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHb6HX3R_QVE&d=EzEu4lfYxXo0QcKw0PjQQdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=c04127eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Hb6HX3R_QVE</a>"},{"pid":"fc8f0944cb716b1c3632c3d4639d6800d90c8924","tid":830880,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T14:21:31.000Z","msg":"唔係 細薯條有成包"},{"pid":"0ff33baa84aca62b9b9f60557642e5786c4335e3","tid":830880,"uid":103237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc8f0944cb716b1c3632c3d4639d6800d90c8924","tid":830880,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T14:21:31.000Z","msg":"唔係 細薯條有成包"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T14:48:11.000Z","msg":"佢特登變半包"},{"pid":"4f2840f4aeea83e3d578d748acbe736dcf8ab1c1","tid":830880,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"r